      • importDirectory

        private static void importDirectory(CommandLine line)
                             throws java.lang.Exception
        Expect directory with subdirectories for each evaluation. Subdirectories must contain following in order for results to be processed:
        • model.txt: libsvm model trained on training set
        • predict.txt: libsvm predictions on test set
        • options.properties: libsvm command line options
